    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and has been kept in a climate-controlled environment, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior retains its original factory scent and shows no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a complete service history and all systems functioning exactly as designed. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
