    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in as-is condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires a thorough diagnostic, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents; the interior also shows heavy wear and tear with several non-functional electronic components. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts.",
