    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to offer this superlative vehicle, presented in impeccable condition. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning buyer an uncompromising driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of distinguished provenance and peerless preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
